{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_零工接活",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·零工接活（拉具路倒，糊口腌臜活）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "零工背尸_done",
              "op": "==",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "done_1"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "n1"
    },
    "done_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "路倒拉走了？成。回头有脏活再寻你。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一个挑着空担的汉子瞅见关二狗，努了努嘴。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "巷尾躺了具路倒，没人认领。拉到义庄去，给你五文。干不干？",
      "next": "n_choice"
    },
    "n_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "jie",
          "text": "「五文就五文。死人钱好挣。」",
          "next": "c_jie"
        },
        {
          "id": "xian",
          "text": "「才五文？……得，拉就拉。」",
          "next": "c_jie"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c_jie": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "关二狗啐了口唾沫搓搓手——上前，过肩，搭手。背尸的老把式，闭着眼都不会错。",
      "next": "n_carry"
    },
    "n_carry": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "carry_ordinary_corpse"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_more"
    },
    "n_more": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "（努嘴往巷子深处）那边还撂着一具，吊死的老汉。一并拉了，再给你五文。",
      "next": "n_carry2"
    },
    "n_carry2": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startPressureHold",
          "params": {
            "id": "carry_ordinary_corpse"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_done"
    },
    "n_done": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "零工背尸_done",
            "value": true
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
